{
  "text": "Human iPSC generation. Three hiPSC lines used in this study were reprogrammed from dermal fibroblasts using non-integrating Sendai virus and the reprogramming factors OCT4, SOX2, KLF4, and C-MYC, as described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . PCBC and P1C1 were reprogrammed from neonatal human dermal fibroblasts (Lonza, USA) 18 . DP3 was reprogrammed from dermal fibroblasts isolated from a patient with type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM) [CITATION_3] .",
